reviewText: It is fun to see the characters vs the Downton Abbey, but to get it you have to watch Downton Abbet first before this one to see the difference characters.
My 6 and 3 year old love it!!
Beyond cute and perfect for a mom and daughter who love Aruther / Downton Abbey. While the story isn't actually of Downton Abbey, it's cute nonetheless.
Will never again buy a PBS Kids video--no ability to skip or fast-forward through previews. Unacceptable.
